metadata.name: 무슨 사정이 있겠지 There Must Be Some Reason #1/1000
metadata.description:
Image generated using AI.

Dedicated to the ones who filled my 2022 with light and grace.

Inspired by these amazing words* from If You Were Light by @baekgahee:

You were like a cigarette that I couldn't finish smoking, you were hands I couldn't slap away, you were the moonlight that chased me, the sunlight I couldn't turn away from. You were all of my luck, and my greatest unhappiness was your absence. I love you. Today is the last time I will say it.

I was before you the purest, often burning, too excited, and greatly demolished. You were a flower in the desert that I wished to make bloom even if I had to pour everything into you, and it was nothing at all to stop breathing lest you fly away.

..  
..  
*This was hastily translated into English from the original Korean without permission. The original Korean words do not belong to me. They belong to @baekgahee or @1riot_of_emotion on Instagram. Love her work. Please don't sue me!
